reviewText: These movies exist and are here. I mean, unless they ALL suck, its a good bet.

The movies on this disc set was ok. Two of the movies on the disc would not play at all,so I don't know if they were ok or not. Instead of trying to return the disc,I just chalked it up to a loss. After having the disc for over two years,the same two movies still won't play. I don't recommend buying used dvd's. Delivery was on time,5 stars for that. The two stars is for the entirety of the disc never would play and after over two years,still doesn't.
